cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper focuses on 3D object detection using point clouds and images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The use of deep learning and feature extraction also suggests the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the analysis of design choices and validation on a dataset suggests the graphics (cs.GR) category.
